WITH _ AS (
                        UPDATE debounce_key
                        SET debounced_times = 0, -- reset debounced_times
                            first_started_at = now(), -- rest
                            previous_job_id = NULL
                        WHERE job_id = $1
                    )
                    UPDATE v2_job_debounce_batch                 
                    SET debounce_batch = nextval('debounce_batch_seq') -- move to new batch
                    WHERE id = $1
